TEXT: The applicant , PERSON , is a NORP national , who was born in DATE and lives in FAC , a village in LOC . The President of the ORG has granted the applicant leave to present her own case . The respondent Government are represented by ORG , ORG at ORG .
The facts of the case , as submitted by the parties , may be summarised as follows .
The applicant had an interest - bearing account in ORG . In DATE , she brought a civil action against the bank because she considered that it had arbitrarily decreased the interest rate .
On DATE , ORG held against the applicant . On DATE , ORG quashed this judgment on appeal and remitted the case for a re - examination .

Having re - examined the case , on CARDINAL DATE the district court partly held for the applicant . On DATE , the regional court upheld this judgment on appeal . On DATE , the district court reopened the case due to discovery of new evidence and remitted the case for a re - examination .

Having re - examined the case , on DATE the district court , composed of CARDINAL professional and CARDINAL lay judges , partly held for the applicant . On DATE , the regional court upheld this judgment on appeal .

On an unspeciﬁed date , ORG applied for supervisory review of the judgments of DATE and CARDINAL DATE . He asked to quash the judgments because of errors of fact and law . On DATE , the Presidium of ORG quashed the judgments and remitted the case for a re - examination .
Having re - examined the case , on DATE the district court held against the applicant . On DATE , the regional court upheld this judgment on appeal .
